snippet.textDisplay: i am surprised to see no one has mentioned in the comments that this teaser is somewhat made in the way that it looks like its an ad from the 90s, like those ARG (alternative reality game) videoes on youtube, if u know what i am talking about. i am pretty sure it could be an ARG probably or they chose this way to just simply promote/tease the music video because it adds up to context in which the music video is made, but either way i am pretty sure there would secrets and easter eggs in the music video (which is out btw) as well and probably a backstory to what TJ 2056 is and whats going around with this so called machine. Anyways, its a pretty creative way to tease a music video, while adding a bit spice into it as well, i liked it. And think about it, if its an ARG, it might Pakistan's first ARG.
